verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H5921"\w* end, \w in|strong="H5921"\w* hymns, \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*.
Hear, O God, \w my|strong="H7725"\w* supplication: \w be|strong="H7725"\w* attentive \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H7725"\w* prayer,

\w To|strong="H7725"\w* thee \w have|strong="H0430"\w* \w I|strong="H2186"\w* cried \w from|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* ends \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* earth: \w when|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H7725"\w* heart \w was|strong="H0430"\w* \w in|strong="H0430"\w* anguish, thou hast exalted \w me|strong="H7725"\w* \w on|strong="H0430"\w* \w a|strong="H7725"\w* rock. Thou hast conducted \w me|strong="H7725"\w*;

\w For|strong="H3588"\w* thou hast \w been|strong="H0776"\w* \w my|strong="H3588"\w* hope; \w a|strong="H3588"\w* tower \w of|strong="H0776"\w* strength against \w the|strong="H3588"\w* face \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* enemy.

\w In|strong="H7200"\w* thy tabernacle \w I|strong="H7200"\w* shall dwell \w for|strong="H7200"\w* ever: \w I|strong="H7200"\w* shall be protected under \w the|strong="H7200"\w* covert \w of|strong="H3196"\w* thy wings.

\w For|strong="H5414"\w* thou, \w my|strong="H5414"\w* \w God|strong="H5414"\w*, hast heard \w my|strong="H5414"\w* prayer: thou hast \w given|strong="H5414"\w* \w an|strong="H5414"\w* inheritance \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w fear|strong="H3373"\w* thy name.

Thou wilt add days \w to|strong="H4616"\w* \w the|strong="H3467"\w* days \w of|strong="H4616"\w* \w the|strong="H3467"\w* \w king|strong="H4616"\w*: \w his|strong="H3467"\w* years even \w to|strong="H4616"\w* generation \w and|strong="H6032"\w* generation.

\w He|strong="H0430"\w* abideth \w for|strong="H0430"\w* ever \w in|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H1696"\w* sight \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*: \w his|strong="H1696"\w* mercy \w and|strong="H0430"\w* truth \w who|strong="H0430"\w* shall search?

So \w will|strong="H3063"\w* I sing \w a|strong="H2710"\w* psalm \w to|strong="H3063"\w* thy name for ever \w and|strong="H3063"\w* ever: that I may pay \w my|strong="H0669"\w* vows \w from|strong="H3063"\w* day \w to|strong="H3063"\w* day.
